panels.title: Latest run | Spark | Structured Streaming vs. Classic

panels.content:
## Warning

This dashboard is used to find performance regressions during Beam development.
It *MUST NOT* be used as a criteria to compare runners or target systems because performance
can change radically depending on your use case, connectors and configuration.

targets.query: SELECT "runtimeMs" FROM "forever"."nexmark_${ID}_sql_${processingType}" WHERE "runner" =~ /^$runner$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "runner"
